text: "Live Fast, Diane Nguyen" is the fifth episode of the first season of American animated television series BoJack Horseman. It was written by Caroline Williams and directed by Joel Moser. The episode was released in the United States, along with the rest of season one, via Netflix on August 22, 2014. Ira Glass, Melissa Leo, and Mike O'Malley provide voices in guest roles in the episode. == Plot == BoJack travels with Diane to New York to meet with his book publisher, but the two take an unexpected side trip to Boston after learning of the death of Diane's father. Meanwhile in LA, Todd accidentally turns BoJack's house into a museum tour of actor David Boreanaz's life. == References == == External links == * "Live Fast, Diane Nguyen" on Netflix * * Category:2014 American television episodes Category:BoJack Horseman episodes
